ğŸ¯ Classification

Comparison-based: Bubble, Insertion, Merge, Quick, Heap

Non-comparison-based: Counting, Radix, Bucket

Stable Sorts: Maintain original order of equal elements

Unstable Sorts: May change order of equal elements



